# hams store .gitignore — keep private state + local overrides out of the repo.
# These patterns mirror the schema-design spec §Store Layout.

# Per-machine state: never shared, regenerated on every apply.
.state/

# Local overrides: machine-specific secrets, auth tokens, API keys.
*.local.yaml
*.local.*

# Common editor / OS cruft users shouldn't have to add manually.
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
